 Dispositioning a lead as Unverified Lead will result in the following:

- The lead is taken out of the automated routing in the Genesys system.
- An "AM - Invalid Lead" activity corresponing to the chosen reason is created in CampusNexus for the student (e.g. "AM - Invalid Lead Sill In High School").
- The school status of the student is changed to "Invalid Lead".
- If the student is not assigned to an admissions representative in CampusNexus, the student is assigned to the agent who dispositioned the call.
- If the student is not assigned to an admissions representative in CampusNexus, all of non-closed, non-cancelled CampusNexus activities prefixed with "AM - " (i.e. admissions) will are reassigned to the agent.
- An "AM - New Lead Notification" activity is created for the agent in CampusNexus.
- Depending on the disposition, [TCPA Consent Retention](https://ultimatemedical.sharepoint.com/sites/MCSUMAIT/SitePages/MCS.aspx?ovuser=afaa0398-6767-478e-8552-1f46c308486c%2Crdeliman%40ultimatemedical.edu&OR=Teams-HL&CT=1673555420665&clickparams=eyJBcHBOYW1lIjoiVGVhbXMtRGVza3RvcCIsIkFwcFZlcnNpb24iOiIyNy8yMzAxMDUwNTYwMCIsIkhhc0ZlZGVyYXRlZFVzZXIiOmZhbHNlfQ%3D%3D#lead-calling-patterns-dispositions-unverified-tcpa-retention) logic may apply, resulting in the consent being removed and the lead being DNC'd in CampusNexus.
- If TCPA Consent was not given originally and not obtained by the agent, or was removed due to [Retain TCPA Consent Logic](https://ultimatemedical.sharepoint.com/sites/MCSUMAIT/SitePages/MCS.aspx?ovuser=afaa0398-6767-478e-8552-1f46c308486c%2Crdeliman%40ultimatemedical.edu&OR=Teams-HL&CT=1673555420665&clickparams=eyJBcHBOYW1lIjoiVGVhbXMtRGVza3RvcCIsIkFwcFZlcnNpb24iOiIyNy8yMzAxMDUwNTYwMCIsIkhhc0ZlZGVyYXRlZFVzZXIiOmZhbHNlfQ%3D%3D#lead-calling-patterns-dispositions-unverified-tcpa-retention), the [Do Not Call Disposition](https://ultimatemedical.sharepoint.com/sites/MCSUMAIT/SitePages/MCS.aspx?ovuser=afaa0398-6767-478e-8552-1f46c308486c%2Crdeliman%40ultimatemedical.edu&OR=Teams-HL&CT=1673555420665&clickparams=eyJBcHBOYW1lIjoiVGVhbXMtRGVza3RvcCIsIkFwcFZlcnNpb24iOiIyNy8yMzAxMDUwNTYwMCIsIkhhc0ZlZGVyYXRlZFVzZXIiOmZhbHNlfQ%3D%3D#lead-calling-patterns-dispositions-dnc) logic is applied. This may also happen for some dispositions where TCPA Consent is automatically removed due to [TCPA Consent Retention](https://ultimatemedical.sharepoint.com/sites/MCSUMAIT/SitePages/MCS.aspx?ovuser=afaa0398-6767-478e-8552-1f46c308486c%2Crdeliman%40ultimatemedical.edu&OR=Teams-HL&CT=1673555420665&clickparams=eyJBcHBOYW1lIjoiVGVhbXMtRGVza3RvcCIsIkFwcFZlcnNpb24iOiIyNy8yMzAxMDUwNTYwMCIsIkhhc0ZlZGVyYXRlZFVzZXIiOmZhbHNlfQ%3D%3D#lead-calling-patterns-dispositions-unverified-tcpa-retention) logic.

​​Unverified Lead - TCPA Consent Retention​

Some Unverified Lead dispositions are configured to not retain TCPA Consent on file. Currently the following dispositions do not retain TCPA Consent (in other words, the consent will be set to "N" for all 6 consent school fields in CampusNexus).

| ​​​​ \*\*Disposition​\*\* |
| --- |
| Does Not Remember School Inquiry |
| ​Bad Name/Phone Match |

