A unique TCG gameplay which empowers strategic thinking.
Various methods to collect artistic, scarce digital collectibles and use them in-game.
User-friendly access for gamers to use the blockchain through seamless on and off ramping.
An enriched marketplace that users can leverage to expand or scale

